_:N1e69c6bfb5ca4e76b64e1f05dc91e00f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Catherine Vaughan <abbr title=\"Companion of the Order of the Bath\">CB</abbr> was appointed as Finance Director General for the Department for Work and Pensions (<abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>) in October 2022.</p>\n\n<p>Before joining <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>, Catherine was the Director General and Chief Operating Officer for the Department for International Trade (<abbr title=\"Department for International Trade\">DIT</abbr>).</p>\n\n<p>Catherine began her career with PricewaterhouseCoopers (<abbr title=\"PricewaterhouseCoopers\">PwC</abbr>) in public sector audit. She is a qualified accountant with the Chartered Institute of Public Finance and Accountancy (<abbr title=\"Chartered Institute of Public Finance and Accountancy\">CIPFA</abbr>). Her subsequent roles have included:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>Director of Finance and Resources for Brighton and Hove City Council</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Chief Finance Officer for the South Downs National Park Authority</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Director of Finance and Business Services at HM Land Registry</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Catherine is a member of the Government Finance Function Leadership Group and leads on SCS talent. She has also been Non-Executive Director on the Board of England Netball.</p>\n\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
