<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/catherine-vaughan> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Catherine Vaughan CB was appointed as Finance Director General for the Department for Work and Pensions ( DWP ) in October 2022. Before joining DWP , Catherine was the Director General and Chief Operating Officer for the Department for International Trade ( DIT ). Catherine began her career with PricewaterhouseCoopers ( PwC ) in public sector audit. She is a qualified accountant with the Chartered Institute of Public Finance and Accountancy ( CIPFA ). Her subsequent roles have included: Director of Finance and Resources for Brighton and Hove City Council Chief Finance Officer for the South Downs National Park Authority Director of Finance and Business Services at HM Land Registry Catherine is a member of the Government Finance Function Leadership Group and leads on SCS talent. She has also been Non-Executive Director on the Board of England Netball."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
